this anime includes romance,action,harem(kinda),horror(lil bit),ecchi(hell yeah O.o)and it is cool to watch and it's name is cool to "Stigma of the Wind" right :D
so lets get in the story about that it's storty isn't that bad and most of the episodes were cool to so story goes like this;
Kazuma Kannagi was considered useless within his family because he could not use Enjutsu, the power to control flames(really a heartless clan they do everything for power).When he was defeated by Ayano Kannagi, one of his relatives, in a bout to decide who the wielder of Enraiha, a sword that was wielded by the family heir, hewas banished from the family. Four years later, he returns, now a master of Fuujutsu, the power to control wind(very cool yeah and he takes his revenge like kicking his fathers but lol :D
